      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;how-to-make-a-mkdocs&#34;&gt;How to make a mkdocs?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Assume you have already set up your Github homepage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
